data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 12/23/23 11AM - 2PM*** PRICE REDUCED WELL BELOW RECENT APPRAISED VALUE!!! Instant Equity! Beautiful Townhome in a wonderful location just off of I215 close to Valley Fair Mall and restaurants! This home is located on a very quiet street with low traffic on a dead-end road. The main level has an open floor plan great for hosting friends and family with a warm fireplace and spacious kitchen and living room. All 3 bedrooms are located on the second floor with a centrally located laundry room. The extra large master bedroom has its own private bathroom with a walk in shower and soaker tub deep enough to relax and soak comfortably in. The back yard is perfect for barbecuing or letting your pets play. Newer carpet and paint throughout.
